 Bismark: WGBS 전처리
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#bismark-wgbs-%ec%a0%84%ec%b2%98%eb%a6%ac">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>#2025-04-21&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="1-build-index">
 1. Build Index
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-build-index">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ bowtie2-build Homo_sapiens.GRCh38.dna.toplevel.fa GRCh38 -p &lt;span class="m">40&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="2-bam-sorting--indexing">
 2. Bam Sorting &amp;amp; Indexing
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-bam-sorting--indexing">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ samtools sort KEB01_1_bismark_bt2_pe.bam -o KEB01_1_bismark_bt2_pe.sorted.bam
